The `POST /amenity/create` endpoint is used to create a new amenity.

### Request Body

- `name` (string, required): The name of the amenity to be created.


### Response

The response is in JSON format and has the following schema:

``` json
{
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
        "message": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "results": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
                "referenceNumber": {
                    "type": "string"
                },
                "name": {
                    "type": "string"
                }
            }
        },
        "code": {
            "type": "integer"
        },
        "error": {
            "type": "boolean"
        }
    }
}

 ```

