### Amenity Update

This endpoint is used to update an amenity with a specific ID.

#### Request Body
- name (string, required): The name of the amenity.

#### Response
The response is a JSON object with the following properties:
- message (string): A message related to the response.
- results (object): An object containing the updated reference number and name.
  - referenceNumber (string): The reference number of the updated amenity.
  - name (string): The name of the updated amenity.
- code (integer): An error code.
- error (boolean): Indicates if an error occurred.

#### JSON Schema
```json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "message": { "type": "string" },
    "results": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "referenceNumber": { "type": "string" },
        "name": { "type": "string" }
      }
    },
    "code": { "type": "integer" },
    "error": { "type": "boolean" }
  }
}
```

